assylias.jbloomberg

Interface RequestBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HistoricalRequestBuilder, IntradayBarRequestBuilder, ReferenceRequestBuilder

    public interface RequestBuilder
    An interface used to create static or historical requests: users of this API should use existing implementations of this interface.

    This interface has been made public for convenience but uses non public types and can't be implemented.
